Rails steps

1. rails new 
2. rails g controller Pages schedule about

--Migrations
3. rails g scaffold entry week:decimal date:string objective:string activity:string reading:string homework:string
4. rake db:migrate
5. restart rails s

—Nested Models—
1. create new model “rails g model …”
2. Create _fields.html.erb
3. Change show and index to display new model
4. update lessons controller new and edit
5. add to lessons model 
6. add to new model
7. add model to form
8. Add to strong params in lessons model


—Adding links to add new objectives —

* be sure to add all variables in strong_params

—-Adding Admin on console—
1. Find the user by “u = User.last
2. “u.update_attribute :admin, 1”
